Class LongStack

    @Generated(date="2017-10-22T12:31:11+0200",
           value="KTypeStack.java")
public class LongStack
extends LongArrayList
    A subclass of LongArrayList adding stack-related utility methods. The top of the stack is at the LongArrayList.size() - 1 element.
